00:06:26.330 --> 00:06:29.050
First, I'm really
happy to be able to be

00:06:29.050 --> 00:06:32.600
making the first announcement
of the Donation API.

00:06:32.600 --> 00:06:35.900
In the words of the developers,
what if gamers everywhere

00:06:35.900 --> 00:06:38.940
could save the real world,
right from within your app,

00:06:38.940 --> 00:06:40.840
powered by Google?

00:06:40.840 --> 00:06:42.450
This is the Donation API.

00:06:42.450 --> 00:06:44.616
It's made for gamers
and generosity.

00:06:44.616 --> 00:06:45.990
And it uses
everything that we've

00:06:45.990 --> 00:06:48.140
learned that users
like when they donate.

00:06:48.140 --> 00:06:51.210
It's got in-app donations,
automatic payment

00:06:51.210 --> 00:06:52.620
processing and billing.

00:06:52.620 --> 00:06:55.220
There are no fees and no spam.

00:06:55.220 --> 00:06:57.940
And it has the ability
for you, the developer,

00:06:57.940 --> 00:07:01.220
to search and support
any US-based nonprofit.

00:07:01.220 --> 00:07:04.100
It's brought to you by the same
group, the Social Good group,

00:07:04.100 --> 00:07:07.370
that has powered donations
for Google.org and the refugee

00:07:07.370 --> 00:07:08.350
