describing this that I'll

00:07:13.640 --> 00:07:17.240
put out and back later for
people to take as they leave.

00:07:17.240 --> 00:07:18.280
Very exciting stuff.

00:07:18.280 --> 00:07:21.320
I'm really happy to be
part of a company that's

00:07:21.320 --> 00:07:23.160
thinking not only of
entertaining people

00:07:23.160 --> 00:07:26.210
but helping them
at the same time.

