become really big

00:44:44.960 --> 00:44:48.190
and known through the power
of the YouTube community.

00:44:48.190 --> 00:44:50.740
The discovery of games
has really changed,

00:44:50.740 --> 00:44:52.820
and you don't need
to spend millions

00:44:52.820 --> 00:44:56.690
